javautils
Class Classes

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--javautils.Classes
public class Classes
extends java.lang.Object

Static utility methods for dealing with classes and reflection.

Note: None of these methods throws checked exceptions. Checked exceptions will be translated to unchecked RuntimeException-exceptions. This makes these methods far more pleasant to use compared to direct use of the Class-class.
